    Object type is Numpy Array. it is not array / list like java. it is vector. we can do addition, subtraction 
    muliplication, etc
In [ ]:
Pandas :
    Object type is Data Frame. useful to load with Pandas. We can do filtering by row/col, join -> like SQL

Matplotlib :
    Useful to draw line chart, scatter plot, histogram and plotting images. 
    Most of the time we have to do one amoung this
In [ ]:
Scipy :
    It is add-on to Numpy. It perform common statistics calculation: PDF, CDF, Sampling, statistical testing.
    Signal processing: Convolution, Fourier transform
    this is most relavant for data sci.
